data.eml:eml: A new species of deepwater wrasse (Labridae: Terelabrus) from the western Pacific Ocean

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fukui, Yoshino, Motomura, Hiroyuki (2015): A new species of deepwater wrasse (Labridae: Terelabrus) from the western Pacific Ocean. Zootaxa 4040 (5): 559-568, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4040.5.4
